Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe War of the Best against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was consumed with unbearable sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, 10 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, Sabo and Luffy were competing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to hunt the big tiger to \Ndecide who would be captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They met a former pirate \N- Naguri who knew Roger,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he agreed to give Luffy \Ntips on how to become a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Battle against the Big Tiger! \NWho is Going to be Captain?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always attack so openly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! What about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put some poisonous \Nmushrooms in the bait tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's big but still a member \Nof the cat family...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means catnip might work, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Luffy is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a week since he left the hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have gone to see him by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the training is too hard for him \Nand he's crying "I wanna go home!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Maybe he's dead already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care about Luffy? \NHe's your younger brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I don't care if \Nhe's crying or he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Stop being stubborn already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Sabo! Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:53.89,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,GRAY TERMINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:07:00.64,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,TIGER
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? A target?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna show you the result of my training!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome! You couldn't \Nreach that far a week ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you beat that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of tips did you give him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just chopping wood \Nwith an ax for me everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe it helped him \Nbuild up his physique.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We challenged Roger, the King \Nof the Pirates, to a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we lost the fight and split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you hate him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hate who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt frustrated for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I lost because I wasn't strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rather feel grateful to him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To someone who beat you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We give up! You win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and cut my head off! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please spare my crew in exchange for my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a man of quite high caliber!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie! There are dozens \Nof people who hate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they really fight with Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the world of pirates, when you \Nlose a fight, you lose your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say that those people fought him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think. They can talk about \Ntheir grudges because they're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get stronger and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what if Roger had a son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be hard to be his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:10:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether he chooses to live a \Nnormal life or as a pirate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he will always be haunted \Nby his father's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be quite hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were his son, I wouldn't \Nwant to become a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that father's name would \Nruin his son's life in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruin his son's life"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking nonsense! \NYou don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you fight me, old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, when you lose a \Nfight, you lose your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Do anything you like with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I want you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that there was a cove.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Hurry up and get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Guys! Hustle, hustle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...boat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it cool?! It's a real pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate ship?! Is this what \NNaguri has been making?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will take forever to make it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you two give me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Give you a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that I can do \Nanything I like with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait a minute! I have to help, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You happened to be here, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not making any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're busy hunting the big tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can give you some pointers \Nto hunt the tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Well, then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do with the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go out to sea, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NTo find my crew that got split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? An old man can't go out to sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn't gonna say that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how old \Nyou are to chase a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what anyone says, \NI'm gonna go out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an old man, full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A promise is a promise. I'll \Ngive you a hand. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will defeat you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so began their training \Nto be pirates with Naguri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through hard labor on the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they gained strength and honed their \Nskills by fighting with Naguri...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...growing both physically and mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seasons come and go but spring \Ncomes late in the Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm gonna win today!\N--I'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! You did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, you guys are only thinking \Nabout getting stronger but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you think that's enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest one among \Nus will become captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The one that kill the tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tiger, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a captain needs to be \Nstrong - that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is more important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A more important thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? How disappointing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't know that \Nyou were here, Ace-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it take to be a captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is more important than being strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I don't know it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't a good captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they called me "Captain" \Nuntil the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I'm still the \Ncaptain of the Naguri Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only your crew's approval \Ncan make you a captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's corny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Naguri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! It's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have done it \Nwithout your help. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Naguri, are you setting sail soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But before that, I have \Nto wrap up your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go and hunt the big tiger today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill him and \Nend this stupid training!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How predictable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're unguarded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta fight me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop resisting, just give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo! Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So heavy! How powerful he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We're not good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only your crew's approval \Ncan make you a captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, give me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not fast enough but we \Ncan do it with Luffy's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Hey, tiger! Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull it as much as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! He's gonna eat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Sabo! \NLure him as far as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ace is gonna be our captain after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked so hard for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm not gonna become captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I didn't beat \Nthe tiger all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make you guys \Nbeg me to become captain sometime soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna beg him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like everything \Nturned out for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I see you, I'm gonna defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep winning until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, they said goodbye to Naguri
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.08,0:22:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Luffy and the other two \Nreturned to life on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you know where he is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.06,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call and tell his father that we found...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.59,0:23:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.43,0:23:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo makes a difficult \Ndecision in order to save
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace and Luffy, who are being held hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sabo is overwhelmed by the suffocating
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lifestyle in High Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as if to deal the final blow, \Nyet another scheme is revealed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.14,0:23:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Freedom Taken Away! The Nobles' \NPlot Closing in on the Brothers!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
